reviews.reviewText: This holder is perfect ! The colors and patterns is super cute but most of all the purpose is what makes it so great ! Hold my cup perfectly and as well fits my phone. Clips my keys on it and can hold my cards and money ! Great for on the go!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits my Tumbler Great
reviews.reviewText: This drink carrier works great for my tumbler and it also fits the 1.5L water bottles. For the water bottles, the velcro comes in handy to secure it, and there is both a short and a long strap for carrying. The big pocket on the outside is big enough for a phone and the small one can hold ID or keys. Pretty cute to go on short hikes with or a walk on the beach. It seems to be made well and the neoprene can insulate cold drinks on those long walks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not just for Stanley Bottles
reviews.reviewText: I should start by saying I do NOT own a Stanley cup. Upon reading the description I was curious to see if this would work for my 32oz Contigo tumbler. I tend to drop it none stop when I take my daily speed walks. Turns out I was right. The velcro strap is very strong so I was able to strap my tumbler in without any issues and it stayed while I was on my walks. This holder comes with two straps, both can clip on to the holder. One can be used to carry the bottle by hand while the other can be used to carry like a crossbody bag or even over the shoulder. There are 3 pockets on the holder. One on the outside can be used to carry ID/DL (or your entire wallet). The first pocket is deep enough ti hold a small hand towel, a flashlight, and maybe one or two other items. The lower, outer netted pocket works great for keys and it has a clip just above the pocket to clip to your keys so as not to fall out. I am also able to clip my hand sanitizer to it. I'm sure this may work with other water bottles, it would just need to be one on the larger side like the one in my photos. I deducted one star because of how thin the stitching is on the section that connects the bag to the holder. I worry it may come loose eventually. Don't mind the dent in my bottle, this is from a drop on one of my previous walks.
